Title: Hot Pollenate-o
Description:
Important to make sure not take too much. Make sure hive healthy so can come back.

Bees eat pollen, yes? So fire bees eat fire pollen? Yes.

Bring fire pollen to bees. Grow strong. Bee productive.

Check edge of hive for flowers bees not get to yet. When catch fire, you got good one.
ObjectivesText: Gather pollen from Pollen Rich Cinderblooms and return it to nearby bees before it goes out.
CompletionText: Just a little bit on fire. You tough, you be okay.
RewardText: Good. Healthy hive make happy wax.
